~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : verify                                    ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : verify <email verification code>

   This command is used to verify your email address for smail 
   auto-forward.  When you set your forwarding email address a 
   verification code is emailed to you.  You must input this code
   to enable smail auto-forwarding.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : set, forwarding
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
